{"article_id":"drwO4cd20UDb769o","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump ' s claim","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that Robert Mueller ' s report is a total exoneration","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"is about to be put to the test","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"as what is known about the special counsel ' s findings swells from four pages to nearly 400 ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"undermining the White House ' s ability","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"to frame the narrative .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Trump has spent recent days trying to soften the ground before Thursday ' s release ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"what matters is Attorney General William P. Barr ' s top-line findings","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"that there was no conspiracy with Russia","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"to subvert the 2016 presidential election","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"and not enough evidence","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"to pursue an obstruction of justice case .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"But the sprawling nature of the 22-month investigation is fueling concerns .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"\" There ' s a little bit of uncertainty","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"because people don ' t really know what ' s in it , \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"a former White House official said .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" You put hundreds of witnesses under oath","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"and you throw all these subpoenas around","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"if there ' s nothing controversial or embarrassing","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that ' s disclosed ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that would be kind of surprising . \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Mr. Trump has acknowledged","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"he hasn ' t read the report","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"even while claiming exoneration .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"That doesn ' t make sense to Democrats ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"who figure","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"they will see either evidence of bad behavior among the 400 pages or redactions so extensive","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that they can blame Mr. Barr of a cover-up .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"\" We have very smart people","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"who will be reading it , \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , California Democrat , said Tuesday in a CNN interview .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Indeed , all of Washington will be studying the report .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"That includes members of the president ' s inner circle","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"who ,","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"according to NBC News ,","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"are fretting about the help","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"they provided to Mr. Mueller .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Fearing retribution from an angry president ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"some of those presidential confidants have been reaching out to the Justice Department","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"to see","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"whether they will be named as collaborators in Mr. Mueller ' s findings .","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"The department has refused to offer any solace .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"One person close to the White House told NBC","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that the hysteria has reached \" breakdown-level anxiety . \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Mr. Trump , meanwhile , has maintained a consistent line .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"\" No Collusion - No Obstruction ! \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"he tweeted Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"The report is expected in the morning ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"igniting a day of study and reaction .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Bookmakers were offering odds","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"on how Mr. Trump would react ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"such as how many times he will use \" exonerate \" or \" exonerated. \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"BookMaker.eu put the over-under at 1.5 times .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"One of Mr. Trump ' s attorneys , Rudolph W. Giuliani , told Politico","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"that the president will release a counter report Thursday","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that runs more than 30 pages .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Yet a former White House official told The","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that the president ' s team isn ' t expecting anything","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that will change the narrative","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"that Mr. Trump was investigated for two years","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"without prosecutors touching him .","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"\" It just may be a bad news cycle , \"","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"the source said .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"\" In 400 pages , there will probably be a few things . \"","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Democrats say","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"they are not sure","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"the nearly 400 pages","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"Mr. Barr has promised","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"will tell them much ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"given that he has said","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"every page has information","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"that could demand redaction","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"to protect classified information , grand jury testimony or ongoing , spinoff investigations .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"\" Just call it The Barr Report .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Just in time for Easter , it will be a crazy quilt of colors","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"designed to cover up key facts","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"and ,","depth":16},{"id":79,"text":"almost more important ,","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"break the flow","depth":16},{"id":81,"text":"- and diminish the power -","depth":16},{"id":82,"text":"of the Mueller Report","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"as written , \"","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"tweeted Elizabeth de la Vega ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"who served as a federal prosecutor for more than two decades .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Rep. Adam B. Schiff , California Democrat and chairman of the House Permanent Select Committee on Intelligence , has said","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Congress must see the full report","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"without redactions .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Mr. Barr has promised to work with Congress on revealing classified information","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"but has resisted demands","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"to break grand jury secrecy .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"Democrats are especially eager to see what Mr. Mueller says about obstruction of justice","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"after the special counsel specifically said","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"the report was not an exoneration .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Mr. Trump , meanwhile , is trying to keep the public focused on Mr. Mueller ' s bigger conclusion","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that there was no criminal conspiracy with Russia","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"- undercutting the narrative","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that launched the lengthy investigation .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"\" The greatest Scam in political history , \"","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"he tweeted Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"\" If the Mainstream Media were honest ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"which they are not ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"this story would be bigger and more important than Watergate .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Someday ! \"","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Outside-the-Beltway analysts said","depth":4},{"id":106,"text":"the president ' s focus could color how the report is seen .","depth":4},{"id":107,"text":"\" It does make it difficult for Democrats to make clear to the public what the president did","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"that did constitute abuse of power .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"It ' s about agenda-setting , \"","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"said Julian E. Zelizer , a politics professor at Princeton University .","depth":4},{"id":111,"text":"- Jeff Mordock and Bailey Vogt contributed to this article .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":222,"right":111,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":216,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":117,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":114,"right":116,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":113,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":3,"right":115,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":133,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":124,"right":132,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":13,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":122,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":7,"right":121,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":8,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":118,"right":119,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":126,"right":131,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":19,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":22,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"par